:::info[How to upgrade]

In case you don't like this new default behavior, you can revert to the former "unlimited feed" behavior with the new `limit: false` feed option:

```js title="docusaurus.config.js"
const blogOptions = {
  feedOptions: {
    // highlight-next-line
    limit: false,
  },
};
```

:::

